  },
  en: {
    title: 'Claim Readiness Checklist',
    h1: 'Check whether your FIDIC claim is ready',
    sub: 'A quick self-check for notices, records, causation, quantum and submission strategy. It is not legal advice; it helps you see whether a claim is ready for review by the Engineer, DAAB or Employer.',
